steps.name: user verifies if item is in cart
user hovers on power tools link
hovers on drills link and click on that
user is navigated to drills page
user clicks on a product
user is navigated to the products page
user increases the quantity of the product
clicks on Add to Cart button
user is navigated to art page
user clicks on Place Order button
user is navigated to Checkout page
user clicks on continue button
user selects the radio button of credit & debit cards/ Net Banking/ EMI
clicks on Place order button
user is navigated to Payment gateway page
user scrolls down and clicks on netbanking option
selects the bank option
clicks on Pay button
user is navigated to confirmation page
user clicks on Success button
order is placed
